ASoC: Intel: bytcr_rt5640: set SSP to I2S mode 2ch

Using the hw_fixup function in order to overwrite the default SSP
setting for Audio DSP port connected to the codec. Instead of
TDM 4ch use I2S 2ch 24 bits.

